r = client.get_product_historic_rates('BTC-USD', start=start, end=end,
    granularity=granularity)
assert type(r) is list
for ticker in r:
    assert all([(type(x) in (int, float)) for x in ticker])
pytest.mark.parametrize('start,end,granularity', [(current_time -
    relativedelta(months=1), current_time, 21600)])
